    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sokogeek</strong> 是一款融入电力元素的推块逻辑游戏。<br>协助 <strong>Flux</strong>，这位机器人吸尘器，通过搭建能量回路来解锁出口，进而逐个突破每个关卡。任务表面简单，实则谜题错综复杂，将极大考验你的空间感知、抽象思维及分析能力。<br>你已准备好充电，迎接挑战了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284120/extras/b4be7c7687e167f830bf92b715153e40.poster.avif?t=1769682672\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284120/extras/b4be7c7687e167f830bf92b715153e40.webm?t=1769682672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284120/extras/b4be7c7687e167f830bf92b715153e40.mp4?t=1769682672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏内含超过125个精心策划的关卡及25个详尽教程，内容编排巧妙，确保进程既清晰又充满成就感。每一谜题均带来全新变化，不断挑战你的解题能力，让你的大脑持续保持敏锐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284120/extras/227ef7d4d827e1815b97fd1481b28643.poster.avif?t=1769682672\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284120/extras/227ef7d4d827e1815b97fd1481b28643.webm?t=1769682672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284120/extras/227ef7d4d827e1815b97fd1481b28643.mp4?t=1769682672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你或许会好奇：‘为何一个机器人吸尘器会成为主角？’<br>嗯……小孩没娘，说起来话长，还是算了吧！</p>",
